  "texts": [
    "Prior to this, research in the creation of dialectal lexicons lies in three categories: the use of online dictionaries, and the use of textual corpora.",
    "Lexicon Induction Using LLMs.A recent approach by Artemova and Plank [2023] performs German dialect lexicon induction using LLMs.",
    "Dialectal DatasetsDatasets based on different data sources (such as social media, and conversation transcripts) and dialects have been reported.",
    "In terms of procuring and labeling these datasets, the following methods have been used: 4.2.1 Recruit native speakers of specific language varieties.",
    "Estival et al. [2014] create a dataset of audio-visual recordings of 1000 speakers of Australian English."
  ]
